{"tid":1695063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"FB換新logo 料在數周內正式啟用","createTime":"2019-11-05T12:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T07:00:29.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53eccab23cdf9c01fe91dbccd8eb50c985803be0","tid":1695063,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"有調查指，只有不足3成美國人得知，社交平台WhatsApp及Instagram是屬於Facebook（美︰FB）旗下。Facebook決定從改用新標誌着手，以提升Facebook品牌的識別度。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook新標誌全部字母以大楷寫成，並有3個版本，分別是藍、綠及紫紅橘色，以對應Facebook同名應用程式，及旗下子公司WhatsApp與Instagram。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Facebook營銷總監盧西奧（Antonio Lucio）表示，希望藉此令公司品牌更清晰，讓用家知道那些產品是來自Facebook。新標誌料在數周內正式啟用</span>。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook自6月起，已在其旗下產品的應用程式內增加「from Facebook」的字樣。而今次改用新標誌，則能進一步讓用家更容易識別Facebook品牌。<br />\n<br />\n美國獨立民調機構皮尤研究中心（Pew Research Center）調查指，僅29%的美國人得知WhatsApp及Instagram是屬於Facebook旗下。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o3H35Sk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3H35Sk.jpg&h=fa276ad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2490665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2490665%2F&d=YDk3w6YkG5F4GHIJWz3fGMorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=8e756cd8\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2490665/</a>"},{"pid":"17026e7236db389f5b0716430ba18a197c594bac","tid":1695063,"uid":238920,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"咁撚奶共<br />\n五星旗底加個F字咪得"},{"pid":"368158e02e153ce9515ce38148b4bf0f884c5673","tid":1695063,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"好快ig同whatsapp都會改埋名叫facebook<br />\n條撚樣朱克伯格想吞併好耐"},{"pid":"6a4d6c8fcb4598f57fa6132f76912f2f54cdebf7","tid":1695063,"uid":9142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-05T12:13:44.000Z","msg":"其他app入面點解要有facebook個logo?"},{"pid":"7952d1c6bb95e22cd4f19af6a45b0771f606a152","tid":1695063,"uid":